snippet.title: Yume Nikki Fangame playthrough - YumeSD ver. 0.02
snippet.description:
Content warning:
-Blood and gore
-Violence
-Loud noises and flashing lights

Read more about this fangame: https://ynfg.yume.wiki/YumeSD_(%E3%82%86%E3%82%81%E3%83%BC%E3%81%99%E3%81%A7%E3%81%83)_
[Download unavailable]

TIMESTAMPS:
0:00 Starting the game, Seeing TV EVENT
4:17 Getting Phablet EFFECT
6:58 Getting Headgear and Happi Coat EFFECTS
13:45 Getting Eraser EFFECT, Seeing Taiko Drum EVENT, Getting Formal and Ponytail EFFECTS
20:14 Seeing Fast Forward EVENT
20:54 Visiting the Star Store
21:50 Getting Kinako Mochi EFFECT
23:20 Buying some speed boost effects, Exploring a Money Bonus Stage
25:44 Getting Head-Holding EFFECT, Exploring a Money Bonus Stage, Seeing Creepy Doll Button EVENT
28:57 Visiting the Star Store, buying more speed boosts, Exploring Monochrome World, seeing Succulent EVENT
33:01 Getting Duck and Dust EFFECTS, Seeing Red Faces EVENT
38:22 Getting Scarecrow EFFECT
41:50 Getting Margarine EFFECT
44:13 Getting IV EFFECT
46:42 Seeing IV EVENT again to raise the number of days logged to at least 70 to unlock 2 NEXUS DOORS
48:48 Getting Seahorse EFFECT, Exploring the House, Seeing Fast Forward event again
53:58 Visiting the Star Store again, buying more speed boosts 
55:09 Exploring Candy World
57:23 Seeing Red Door EVENT
59:03 Seeing Wedding EVENT
1:01:03 Seeing Pizza EVENT
1:03:56 Seeing Robo Hotel EVENT
1:06:25 Seeing ENDING
1:08:47 Tsukiai gets ready to leave the house, returning back to the title screen
